law.history: Repealed 2015 Ky. Acts ch. 117, sec. 17, effective June 24, 2015. -- Amended 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 85, sec. 55, effective July 15, 2010. -- Created 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 346, sec. 10, effective July 15, 1986.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Nurse midwifery permits not to be issued after January 1, 1986 -- Current permits may be reissued -- Use of title "advanced practice registered nurse" regulated.
